hy Nissan Is Selling Its Iconic Yokohama Headquarters\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/news/why-nissan-is-selling-its-yokohama-headquarters\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Nissan headquarters in Yokohama, Japan\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(min-width: 790px) 375px, (min-width: 768px) calc(50vw - 24px), calc(100vw - 24px)\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 1200w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1920,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 1920w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_2048,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 2048w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg 3840w\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTAwMjM2/gettyimages-899605904.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/article\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"amg-s-ceo-says-its-future-models-will-be-different\"\u003eAMG’s CEO says its future models will be “different”\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eIn the same interview, Shiebe noted that AMG’s future cars will be distinctively AMG. When asked about how its future EVs would distinguish themselves among the lineup, he noted that “There won’t be such a difference between them, because all these cars need to be an AMG first and then an ICE or EV second. When you buy an AMG, you buy the performance, the emotion.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eHe also added that making AMG’s offerings visually different than mainstream \u003ca href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/mercedes-benz/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eMercedes-Benz\u003c/a\u003e models is as important as ever, noting that its buyers “love the distinctive AMG look and the differentiation it brings. Our future cars will be more expressive in that dimension. If you look into the future, I would say you can expect cars that will be more visually differentiated—AMG will be doubling down on design; our design language will be more expressive.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"MSCHF x AMG: Not for Automotive Use\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2992\" height=\"1994\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" sizes=\"(min-width: 750px) 750px, calc(100vw - 60px)\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 1200w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1920,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 1920w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_2048,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 2048w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png 3840w\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwODk3NTM4/hangerdetail-897538.png\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"final-thoughts\"\u003eFinal thoughts\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eUltimately, buyers buy with their wallets, regardless of the badge on the hood, grille, and trunk lid. We live in complicated times, where automakers must juggle tariffs, electrification, and emissions regulations, as well as a vocal buying public that can drop the ball at any time. I don’t think the decision to use a turbo-four was entirely made in a vacuum, but if the Affalterbach boffins are aware of the feedback to their product, they would probably know by now.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003csection\u003e\u003carticle\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca aria-label=\"View post: BYD Passes Tesla in Europe as Chinese EV Maker Gains Ground\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/news/byd-passes-tesla-in-europe-as-chinese-ev-maker-gains-ground\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"The exterior of a BYD showroom, operated by Schiller Auto, in Budapest, Hungary.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(min-width: 790px) 375px, (min-width: 768px) calc(50vw - 24px), calc(100vw - 24px)\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEzMjMzNDg3OTU4Nzc5MzQz/a-byd-co-showroom-as-chinese-ev-giant-plans-hungary-factory.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEzMjMzNDg3OTU4Nzc5MzQz/a-byd-co-showroom-as-chinese-ev-giant-plans-hungary-factory.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEzMjMzNDg3OTU4Nzc5MzQz/a-byd-co-showroom-as-chinese-ev-giant-plans-hungary-factory.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEzMjMzNDg3OTU4Nzc5MzQz/a-byd-co-showroom-as-chinese-ev-giant-plans-hungary-factory.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEzMjMzNDg3OTU4Nzc5MzQz/a-byd-co-showroom-as-chinese-ev-giant-plans-hungary-factory.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/MjEzMjMzNDg3OTU4Nzc5MzQz/a-byd-co-showro